{"type":"message","id":"9639422f","parentId":"b1ae0992","timestamp":"2026-03-20T20:51:41.631Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-03-21 04:51 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索以下行业的最新动态（2026年3月）：\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n要求：\n- 搜索近期的行业政策、市场动态、技术趋势、标杆案例\n- 整理3-5条最关键的行业信息\n- 每条信息包含：标题、摘要（50字内）、来源\n- 最终将结果输出为JSON格式，包含数组learning_notes\n\n返回格式示例：\n{\"learning_notes\": [{\"title\": \"xxx\", \"summary\": \"xxx\", \"source\": \"xxx\"}]}"}],"timestamp":1774039901629}}
{"type":"message","id":"66d01a2a","parentId":"9639422f","timestamp":"2026-03-20T20:51:45.574Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me search for the latest industry news in March 2026 for these four industries. I'll use the web search skill to find current information.","thinkingSignature":"f2c75b0e10c05ccf41e7df11eb091d6a6e9f54aef431a8e46c6d680c6568d61f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_njy0tv11mmib_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":70,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":31330,"totalTokens":31517,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.000084,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0037595999999999997,"total":0.0038786999999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774039901631}}
{"type":"message","id":"86198888","parentId":"66d01a2a","timestamp":"2026-03-20T20:51:45.580Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_njy0tv11mmib_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774039905577}}
{"type":"message","id":"a005d82f","parentId":"86198888","timestamp":"2026-03-20T20:51:51.215Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll search for each of the four industries. Let me run multiple searches in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"3f5fec816541abf878a6624a1ec11370bbd9ae1876e002868a8e97c0983bed85"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ld7y1xft7ju0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026年3月 政策 市场动态 技术趋势\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ld7y1xft7ju0_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 2026年3月 行业动态 技术趋势 市场\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ld7y1xft7ju0_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 2026年3月 行业动态 市场趋势\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ld7y1xft7ju0_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务 2026年3月 行业动态 市场趋势 政策\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":886,"output":288,"cacheRead":31146,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32320,"cost":{"input":0.0002658,"output":0.0003456,"cacheRead":0.00093438,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00154578}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774039905580}}
